{
    "publish_date": "2015-03-20T00:00:01.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT4M59S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "- Someone should push my cart\nfor me, you know?", 
            "dur": "2.567", 
            "start": "0.333"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m a celebrity.\n[laughter]", 
            "dur": "2.033", 
            "start": "2.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "male announcer:\n&quot;Repeat After Me.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.1", 
            "start": "4.933"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Tuesdays on ABC.", 
            "dur": "2.767", 
            "start": "6.033"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- There&#39;s a kindergarten teacher", 
            "dur": "1.133", 
            "start": "8.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "from Albuquerque, New Mexico\nin our audience.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "9.933"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I want you to meet her.\nSonya Romero, come on down!", 
            "dur": "2.833", 
            "start": "11.933"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You teach kindergarten,\nand what is the question--", 
            "dur": "1.934", 
            "start": "14.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the first question you ask\nevery morning?", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "16.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- So I ask my kids if they&#39;ve\neaten that morning,", 
            "dur": "3.833", 
            "start": "19.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if they need anything to wear\nor need to brush their teeth", 
            "dur": "3.7", 
            "start": "23.033"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or comb their hair.", 
            "dur": "1.533", 
            "start": "26.733"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We usually spend about the first\nhour of our morning", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "28.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "getting ready for our day\nto learn, and I--", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "30.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I feel like, as educators, we&#39;re\nsort of first responders, so...", 
            "dur": "4.2", 
            "start": "32.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- And so--and you&#39;ve taken in\ntwo foster kids.", 
            "dur": "3.334", 
            "start": "36.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have two children\nof your own, right?", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "40"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I have one son.\n- One son.", 
            "dur": "1.533", 
            "start": "41.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He&#39;s in the audience, I think.\n- He is, he is.", 
            "dur": "1.933", 
            "start": "43.133"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- So, he was just watching--", 
            "dur": "1.234", 
            "start": "45.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "7.3", 
            "start": "46.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you have one son, and--\naren&#39;t you proud of your mom?", 
            "dur": "2.8", 
            "start": "53.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Doesn&#39;t--isn&#39;t she cool?", 
            "dur": "1.266", 
            "start": "56.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Yeah, I&#39;m very proud.\n- Yeah, she&#39;s--", 
            "dur": "2.734", 
            "start": "57.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She&#39;s an amazing woman.\nSo then you took in", 
            "dur": "2.833", 
            "start": "60.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "two foster children--\ntell everyone the story of that.", 
            "dur": "3.333", 
            "start": "63.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- So they were two of\nmy former students.", 
            "dur": "2.234", 
            "start": "66.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They were in my class,\nand, um,", 
            "dur": "2.266", 
            "start": "68.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Child Protective Services\nhad come that day", 
            "dur": "2.334", 
            "start": "71.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I think any time Child\nProtective Services comes to,", 
            "dur": "3.833", 
            "start": "73.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you know, a school, you know\nit&#39;s never a good thing.", 
            "dur": "3.233", 
            "start": "77.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they were there that day.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "80.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was a Friday\nand I got a call,", 
            "dur": "2.134", 
            "start": "82.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because they had requested if\nI would have them for 48 hours,", 
            "dur": "3.166", 
            "start": "84.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I said, &quot;Of course.&quot;\nThey&#39;re beautiful children,", 
            "dur": "3.534", 
            "start": "87.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and so I sent my family out\nto get--we had nothing,", 
            "dur": "3.366", 
            "start": "91.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so we got toothbrushes and\njammies and underwear", 
            "dur": "2.534", 
            "start": "94.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and brushes and, uh,\nthey&#39;ve been with us ever since.", 
            "dur": "3.833", 
            "start": "97.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- For how long now?\n- Six months.", 
            "dur": "1.533", 
            "start": "101.033"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Six months.\n- Six months.", 
            "dur": "0.967", 
            "start": "102.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Good for you.\nYou&#39;re amazing.", 
            "dur": "1.467", 
            "start": "103.533"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[cheers and applause]\n- Thank you.", 
            "dur": "1.033", 
            "start": "105"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- You&#39;re amazing.\n- Thank you.", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "106.033"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "5.667", 
            "start": "107.733"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- We have a little surprise\nfor you,", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "113.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you look at that monitor\nright there.", 
            "dur": "1.466", 
            "start": "115.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Okay.", 
            "dur": "1.2", 
            "start": "116.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[&quot;I Bet My Life&quot;\nby Imagine Dragons plays ]", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "117.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Miss Sonya inspires me", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "119.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because she&#39;s just fun.", 
            "dur": "2.067", 
            "start": "121.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- When we say we love her,\nshe says she--she loves us back.", 
            "dur": "5.133", 
            "start": "123.333"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I still visit her, just to\nsay hi and give her a hug.", 
            "dur": "4.1", 
            "start": "128.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Makes me feel, like, comfort,\nkind of.", 
            "dur": "2.667", 
            "start": "132.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- And I want to be like her\nwhen I grow up.", 
            "dur": "1.633", 
            "start": "135.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I want to be able to make\neveryone feel like they&#39;re equal", 
            "dur": "3.267", 
            "start": "136.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they all have some part in\nthe world that they can improve,", 
            "dur": "2.467", 
            "start": "140.133"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they can make it a better place,", 
            "dur": "1.633", 
            "start": "142.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Miss Sonya is the embodiment\nof all the best", 
            "dur": "3.033", 
            "start": "144.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that goes on here the school.", 
            "dur": "1.2", 
            "start": "147.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- The way she connects\nwith students", 
            "dur": "2.267", 
            "start": "148.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is--is really authentic.", 
            "dur": "2.467", 
            "start": "150.733"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She decides what their\nstrengths are,", 
            "dur": "3.066", 
            "start": "153.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and she really kind of pulls\nthat out of them.", 
            "dur": "2.934", 
            "start": "156.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Teachers are supposed to have\nthese professional boundaries,", 
            "dur": "2.666", 
            "start": "159.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and whatnot, but she really--\nher heart has no boundaries.", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "161.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- She starts every morning\nmaking sure all of her students", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "165.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have clean clothes\nand they&#39;ve eaten breakfast.", 
            "dur": "3.3", 
            "start": "168.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Sonya was here late one night,", 
            "dur": "2.667", 
            "start": "171.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we had two children\nin crisis,", 
            "dur": "2.933", 
            "start": "174.133"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the social worker\ncould not find", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "177.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "an emergency placement\nfor those children.", 
            "dur": "2.1", 
            "start": "178.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Without a second thought,\nSonya said, &quot;I will take them.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.167", 
            "start": "180.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Well, a weekend became a week,", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "184.133"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "became &quot;I&#39;ll just help them\nthrough the holidays,&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.167", 
            "start": "186.333"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and now she is full-on\ntheir foster mom.", 
            "dur": "3.133", 
            "start": "189.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Sonya says, over and over,\n&quot;This is not about me.", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "192.633"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is about all of us.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.867", 
            "start": "195.133"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[music resumes, singing]\nSo I, I bet my life--", 
            "dur": "3.433", 
            "start": "197"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[applause]\n- Thank you for all that you do.", 
            "dur": "2.133", 
            "start": "200.433"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to make the world\na better place.", 
            "dur": "1.634", 
            "start": "202.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Thank you for being awesome.", 
            "dur": "1.866", 
            "start": "204.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Thank you for teaching me,", 
            "dur": "2.034", 
            "start": "206.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m really happy that you did.", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "208.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(all)\nWe love you, Miss Sonya!", 
            "dur": "4.266", 
            "start": "210.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "4.434", 
            "start": "214.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Thank you so much.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "219.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[crying]", 
            "dur": "1.533", 
            "start": "221.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Well, now I&#39;m crying too,\nbecause--", 
            "dur": "2.433", 
            "start": "222.733"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[laughter]\nIt&#39;s sweet as can be,", 
            "dur": "1.467", 
            "start": "225.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and your son&#39;s crying--\nyou&#39;re an amazing woman.", 
            "dur": "2.267", 
            "start": "226.633"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now we&#39;re gonna--we want\nto talk about the school, and--", 
            "dur": "5.066", 
            "start": "228.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Tell everyone the name\nof it again,", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "233.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because I want people\nto help it.", 
            "dur": "2.067", 
            "start": "235.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Lew Wallace Elementary\nin downtown Albuquerque, NM.", 
            "dur": "3.367", 
            "start": "237.533"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Go to our website if you--\n&#39;cause when you hear", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "240.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the budget that they have, and\nwhat comes out of her pocket--", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "243.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we want to help this school,\nwe want to help these kids.", 
            "dur": "2.766", 
            "start": "245.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we&#39;re gonna help you\nwhen we come back.", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "248.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re busy and you&#39;re\nspending a lot of money,", 
            "dur": "2.234", 
            "start": "250.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because you care about\nthese kids--", 
            "dur": "1.633", 
            "start": "252.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Absolutely.\n- And so Target wants to", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "254.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "help you, they want to help.", 
            "dur": "1.567", 
            "start": "255.833"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I know that you&#39;ve gotten\na donation for $100,", 
            "dur": "3.133", 
            "start": "257.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "from someone who was\na good Samaritan.", 
            "dur": "1.833", 
            "start": "260.533"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You turned around and gave\nthat $100", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "262.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to a woman you saw crying\non a bench.", 
            "dur": "2.167", 
            "start": "263.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So Target wants to give you\n$10,000.", 
            "dur": "2.467", 
            "start": "266.133"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Oh, my God.\n[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "1.233", 
            "start": "268.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "269.833"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- This is for you.", 
            "dur": "1.133", 
            "start": "272.433"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "2.167", 
            "start": "273.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And...", 
            "dur": "1", 
            "start": "275.733"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "5.667", 
            "start": "276.733"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And because I know\nwhat kind of person you are,", 
            "dur": "2.033", 
            "start": "282.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you think you&#39;re going to\nuse this $10,000", 
            "dur": "2.1", 
            "start": "284.433"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to help other people,\nthey also want to give", 
            "dur": "2.433", 
            "start": "286.533"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "$10,000 to Lew Wallace\nElementary School,", 
            "dur": "2.634", 
            "start": "288.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so you&#39;re gonna get another--", 
            "dur": "1.466", 
            "start": "291.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Oh, my gosh!\n[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "1.434", 
            "start": "293.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[cheers and applause]", 
            "dur": "4.9", 
            "start": "294.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Oh, my--\n- So one&#39;s for you,", 
            "dur": "1.2", 
            "start": "299.4"
        }, 
        {
